    "description": "Shong is a &quot;chess-lite&quot;, a simple take on the abstract strategy genre of games.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHere you take control of four lone pieces and attempt to &quot;Shong&quot; your opponent. How do you &quot;Shong&quot; your opponent? You trap their king or move your king to the other side of the board.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSound simple? There's a twist. Each time you move a piece, the piece will flip between two movement patterns creating an extra layer of complexity when thinking multiple moves ahead.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlay tournament mode and be greeted with seven different AI personalities, each one complete with a unique strategy.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nChallenge your friends to multiplayer online or locally.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nCan you become the ultimate Shong champion?",
